  **<span class="skrw-link" data-action="click->skrw-form#toggleMarkdown">
    How to use markdown (md) text format?
  </span>**

<pre>
• put returns between paragraphs
• for single linebreaks add two spaces at the end of line
• wrap <em>_italic text_</em> with underscores
• wrap <strong>**bold text**</strong> with double asteriks
• make links using…
  … https://example.com for simple links
  … [text](https://address.com) for text links
• make regular lists using dashes like…
  - List Item 1
  - List Item 2
  …
• make numbered lists using numbers with a dot
  1. List Item 1
  2. List Item 2
  …
</pre>
